text: Sandgates On Cat Creek is a historic home located at Oakville, St. Mary's County, Maryland. It is a -story, three-bay frame structure with brick ends built between 1740 and 1780. It is one of the best and most authentic restorations in Southern Maryland. It was listed on the National Register of Historic Places in 1978. ==References== ==External links== *, including undated photo, at Maryland Historical Trust * Category:Houses on the National Register of Historic Places in Maryland Category:Houses in St. Mary's County, Maryland Category:Houses completed in 1750 Category:Historic American Buildings Survey in Maryland Category:National Register of Historic Places in St. Mary's County, Maryland
